tems-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building2 lucide-building-2 w-7 h-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 12h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 8h4\"></path><path d=\"M14 21v-3a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v3\"></path><path d=\"M6 10H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2\"></path><path d=\"M6 21V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2 group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors\">Business Insurance</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 line-clamp-2\">Protect your business from unforeseen risks with comprehensive coverage.</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-primary\">Custom Plans</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-secondary opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div></a></div></div><div class=\"text-center mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-secondary font-medium hover:gap-3 transition-all\" href=\"/insurance\">View All Insurance Plans<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><span class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-4\">Why Choose Us</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6\">Your Trusted Financial Partner</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8\">At KalyaniFinance, we believe in making financial services accessible, transparent, and customer-friendly. Our commitment to excellence has made us a preferred choice for thousands of Indians.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-accent text-sm font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-4 h-4 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg>Channel Partner</div></div></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Quick Approval</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Get loan approval within 24 hours with minimal documentation and instant disbursal.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-percent w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"19\" x2=\"5\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><circle cx=\"6.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"17.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Best Interest Rates</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Enjoy the lowest interest rates in the market with transparent pricing and no hidden charges.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-check w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"m9 15 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Easy Documentation</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Simple paperwork with digital KYC process. Upload documents online from anywhere.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">100% Secure</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Bank-grade security for all your transactions. Your data is safe with us.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">24/7 Support</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Our expert team is available round the clock to assist you with any queries.</p></div><div class=\"p-6 rounded-2xl bg-card border border-border hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-badge-check w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3.85 8.62a4 4 0 0 1 4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 6.74 0 4 4 0 0 1 4.78 4.78 4 4 0 0 1 0 6.74 4 4 0 0 1-4.77 4.78 4 4 0 0 1-6.75 0 4 4 0 0 1-4.78-4.77 4 4 0 0 1 0-6.76Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2\">Trusted by Millions</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Over 50,000+ satisfied customers across India trust us for their financial needs.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center\"><div class=\"order-2 lg:order-1\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-3xl border border-border p-8 shadow-lg\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calculator w-6 h-6 text-primary\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"16\" height=\"20\" x=\"4\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"16\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"14\" y2=\"18\"></line><path d=\"M16 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path></svg></div><di