0px)\"><a class=\"group block h-full\" href=\"/blog/home-loan-vs-rent\"><div class=\"aspect-[16/10] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/20 to-purple-500/20 mb-5 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-6xl font-bold text-foreground/5\">K</span></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-accent text-xs font-medium text-foreground\">Home Loan</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg>6 min read</div></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors line-clamp-2\">Home Loan vs. Rent: Which is Better for You?</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground line-clamp-2 mb-3\">A comprehensive comparison to help you decide whether to buy a home with a loan or continue renting.</p><span class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">May 10, 2026</span></a></article></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 lg:py-28 bg-foreground\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><span class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-4\">Get In Touch</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-background mb-6\">Ready to Start Your Financial Journey?</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-background/70 leading-relaxed mb-8\">Fill out the form and our financial experts will get back to you within 24 hours with personalized solutions for your needs.</p><div class=\"space-y-4\"><di